 "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511011, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 所以他们为啥不出国啊，我是因为绩点不高也没论文，所以苟直博了…", "timestamp": 1631676988, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511153, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511011, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 所以你的意思是国内学术要崛起了？", "timestamp": 1631677264, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511161, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511119, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 没论文呗，贵系有几个论文多到可以稳保top10的…", "timestamp": 1631677298, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511176, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511161, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 确实不多", "timestamp": 1631677386, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511181, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511176, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 我认为拍着胸脯说明年美国top10见的真就屈指可数", "timestamp": 1631677439, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511207, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511181, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 确实", "timestamp": 1631677633, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511208, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "看来想出国的都在树洞上了，各位抓紧润吧", "timestamp": 1631677643, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511353, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "贵九非常慌，求求前面大佬们赶紧出国不然孩子没学上了", "timestamp": 1631678816, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511589, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511153, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 哈？不会真有人觉得贵系本科生毕业之后读研究生都是想着将来走学术道路吧。", "timestamp": 1631680917, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511683, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511589, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 出国读硕士在那边工作一年学费全回来了，为啥不去呢？", "timestamp": 1631681446, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511721, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511683, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 对贵系靠前学生来说，可以，但没必要。", "timestamp": 1631681837, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511734, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511683, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 不同人的条件不同，可行的选择不同，效用函数不同。有些人眼中的最佳出路只是另一些人眼里的保底。", "timestamp": 1631681925, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511768, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511683, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 或者可以理解为 贵系靠前的学生基本上都有信心在国内过上舒服的生活。出国的更多是真正有学术追求一心想找教职的。", "timestamp": 1631682238, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511801, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511768, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 但是国内根本没有那么多科研岗位给博士生（或者说博士生宁愿去当个算法工程师也不当researcher。。）这多浪费呢 算法工程师到头一年200税前吧。。", "timestamp": 1631682600, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511820, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511801, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 人家自己不觉得浪费啊，而且人家自己难道不比你清楚同实验室学长找到了什么工作。。。", "timestamp": 1631682736, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511843, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511820, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 这在一定程度上证明了贵系前面同学还是随大溜。。大家都保研就保", "timestamp": 1631682923, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511847, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511820, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 想问一下所谓贵系学生国内最好的出路是什么呀？", "timestamp": 1631682954, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511851, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511820, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 为什么我觉得拿百万package的屈指可数呢", "timestamp": 1631682994, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511977, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511843, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 当然随大流，高考我还随大流呢", "timestamp": 1631684153, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511993, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511977, "tag": null, "text": "Re Olivia: 哈哈哈哈，确实", "timestamp": 1631684363, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512038, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Paul", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511820, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: grace为自己的辩护是合理的 不过不用拉上所有“贵系靠前的同学” …", "timestamp": 1631684906, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512519, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2512038, "tag": null, "text": "Re Paul: 假定贵系靠前的同学不傻，那根据事实比例，我感觉我的推理没毛病。。。当然，也可以解释为贵系靠前的同学很多都比较傻地跟风，选了不那么有利于自己的选择，你开心就好。", "timestamp": 1631690583, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512610, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511847, "tag": null, "text": "Re Nathan: 最好的出路根据个人兴趣和能力，因人而异。另外，贵系同学有些人并不觉得只有百万package才是好的出路。", "timestamp": 1631691465, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512842, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2512610, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 你是贵系的嘛", "timestamp": 1631693777, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512892, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2512610, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 我这么说，只考虑读博士（毕竟硕士太少了），在国内读博士几乎不太可能在985（每年个位数）做学术，而在国外top30读个phd基本有些成果都能回来至少985当老师；读博士之后就业在国外显著工资更高；除了这些我只能认为g君说的其他道路就是从政了。但是我很好奇贵系前50的同学有多少愿意从政的，至少据我观察应该不超过两只手吧。。", "timestamp": 1631694296, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512909, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2512519, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 我觉得没人会做对自己不利的选择，只是他们看到的东西有局限。树洞风气就是run，可能大家只看到工资高房子大没看见文化政治差异；贵系同学选择国内读博也不代表他们未来的发展只在国内，只是现在（政治、疫情等因素下）权衡之后较好的结果。", "timestamp": 1631694502, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512967, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2512892, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 成果差不多的条件下，清华cs博士去985教职并不比国外top30难", "timestamp": 1631695352, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2512984, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Queen", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2512892, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 有这么夸张吗", "timestamp": 1631695536, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513003, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2512892, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 即使在贵系，大部分青年教师也都是土博，只有叉院是例外", "timestamp": 1631695749, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513077, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Richard", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2513003, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 不不不，我贵系今年找教职，难度比国外博士多太多了，很多学校门槛不要国内博士，除非做博后。比如清北人浙", "timestamp": 1631696398, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513263, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2513003, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 你说的是现在的，他们都是十年前开始读的博士了。", "timestamp": 1631698052, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513305, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2513263, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 我说的就是这两年入职的助理教授和助理研究员啊，说实话真没看到几个国外phd，可能他们都不想回国吧", "timestamp": 1631698381, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513496, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Richard", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2513305, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 都是博后了", "timestamp": 1631699934, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513515, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Susan", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "9/50路过", "timestamp": 1631700186, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513525, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2512892, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 很多贵系同学会认为国内读博将来在国内赚的工资已经够用过得够舒服了，没必要再去国外赚更多的钱。。。大三年级选择读博的同学，不出意外，会和自己联系的导师交流过，和同学交流过，和学长、班主任交流过，然后得出了一个足够舒服的选择。。。你能够理解很多贵系同学想赚钱，那应该也能理解很多贵系同学并不打算最大化能赚的钱，够用就行了..... ", "timestamp": 1631700314, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513527, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2513496, "tag": null, "text": "Re Richard: 感觉博后就是接着被老师“压榨”几年。。", "timestamp": 1631700331, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513530, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Susan", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2511683, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: susan就是这样觉得 不喜欢科研，博士五年的机会成本太大了", "timestamp": 1631700366, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513531, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2513525, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 这样的话什么时候能翻身做资本家啊（不会有人不想做资本家吧", "timestamp": 1631700375, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513538, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2513531, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 贵系很多人出去之后就是舒舒服服当高级打工人啊，还挺多人本科毕业去工作呢，也没啥不好的。。。。", "timestamp": 1631700434, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2513543, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 479394, "reply_to": 2513525, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 但是你没觉得在国内读博并没有显著增加收入嘛，nb的人本科